<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7119294>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Live coloration of Gymnothorax poikilospilus sp. nov.. (A) daytime, paratype, TOU-AE 5112; (B) nighttime, front, paratype, TOU-AE 5112; behind, holotype, TOU-AE 0645, showing the obvious dark patches and fine greyish-white fin margins." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7119294/files/figure.png" ;
